Ajman Police discusses cooperation with the Consulate-General of the Republic of Singapore in Dubai

Al Khaleej – Ajman Police discussed cooperation with the Consulate-General of the Republic of Singapore in Dubai - Sunday, 12 May 2019– Page 13 – Staff Report

Ministry of Foreign Affairs received Credentials of Singapore Consul-General

Dubai - Abdulrahamn Ghanem Al Mutaiwee, Director of the Dubai office of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs and International Cooperation, has received the credentials of the new Consul-General of the Republic of Singapore in Dubai and Northern Emirates. Al Mutaiwee welcomes the Consul-General and praised the political, economic and trade relations between the two friendly countries and wished him success in his new assignment.
